">Zeigt ein Navigationsmen\u00fc mit Navigationselementen als Pills an.</Description><Description language-id="ca_ES">Mostra un men\u00fa de navegaci\u00f3 amb elements de navegaci\u00f3 que es mostren com a c\u00e0psules.</Description><Description language-id="ar_SA">\u064a\u0639\u0631\u0636 \u0642\u0627\u0626\u0645\u0629 \u062a\u0646\u0642\u0644 \u0628\u0639\u0646\u0627\u0635\u0631 \u062a\u0646\u0642\u0644 \u064a\u062a\u0645 \u0639\u0631\u0636\u0647\u0627 \u0641\u064a \u0634\u0643\u0644 \u0623\u0632\u0631\u0627\u0631.</Description><Description language-id="fi_FI">N\u00e4ytt\u00e4\u00e4 navigointivalikon navigointikohteet pillerein\u00e4.</Description><Description language-id="en_US">Displays a navigation menu with navigation items shown as pills.</Description><Description language-id="zh_CN">\u663e\u793a\u5bfc\u822a\u83dc\u5355\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u5bfc\u822a\u9879\u663e\u793a\u4e3a\u836f\u4e38\u3002</Description><Description language-id="es_ES">Muestra un men\u00fa de navegaci\u00f3n con elementos de navegaci\u00f3n que se muestran como globos.</Description><Description language-id="nl_NL">Geeft een navigatiemenu weer met navigatie-items in de vorm van pillen.</Description></root>','ftl','<#include "${templatesPath}/NAVIGATION-MACRO-FTL" />\u000a\u000a<#if !entries?has_content>\u000a\u0009<#if themeDisplay.isSignedIn()>\u000a\u0009\u0009<div class="alert alert-info">\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009<@liferay.language key="there-are-no-menu-items-to-display" />\u000a\u0009\u0009</div>\u000a\u0009</#if>\u000a<#else>\u000a\u0009<#assign\u000a\u0009\u0009portletDisplay = themeDisplay.getPortletDisplay()\u000a\u000a\u0009\u0009navbarId = "navbar_" + portletDisplay.getId()\u000a\u0009/>\u000a\u000a\u0009<div id="${navbarId}">\u000a\u0009\u0009<ul aria-label=<@liferay.language key="site-pages" />" class="nav nav-pills navbar-site" role="menubar">\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009<#assign navItems = entries />\u000a\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009<#list navItems as navItem>\u000a\u0009\u0009\u0009\u