0dc\u30bf\u30f3\u5f62\u5f0f\u306e\u30c9\u30ed\u30c3\u30d7\u30c0\u30a6\u30f3\u3067\u30ca\u30d3\u30b2\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3 \u30e1\u30cb\u30e5\u30fc\u3092\u8868\u793a\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002</Description><Description language-id="fr_FR">Affiche un menu de navigation d\u00e9roulant dont les \u00e9l\u00e9ments sont affich\u00e9s sous la forme de boutons.</Description><Description language-id="hu_HU">Megjelen\u00edt egy leny\u00edl\u00f3 navig\u00e1ci\u00f3s men\u00fct, amelyben a gy\u00f6k\u00e9rszint\u0171 men\u00fcpontok gombokk\u00e9nt jelennek meg.</Description><Description language-id="de_DE">Zeigt ein Dropdown-Navigationsmen\u00fc mit Root-Men\u00fcelementen als Schaltfl\u00e4chen an.</Description><Description language-id="ca_ES">Mostra un men\u00fa de navegaci\u00f3 desplegable els elements de men\u00fa arrel que es mostren com a botons.</Description><Description language-id="ar_SA">\u064a\u0639\u0631\u0636 \u0642\u0627\u0626\u0645\u0629 \u062a\u0646\u0642\u0644 \u0645\u0646\u0633\u062f\u0644\u0629 \u062a\u062d\u062a\u0648\u064a \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0639\u0646\u0627\u0635\u0631 \u0642\u0627\u0626\u0645\u0629 \u062c\u0630\u0631 \u062a\u0638\u0647\u0631 \u0643\u0623\u0632\u0631\u0627\u0631.</Description><Description language-id="fi_FI">N\u00e4ytt\u00e4\u00e4 pudotusnavigointivalikon juurivalikon kohdat esitettyn\u00e4 painikkeina.</Description><Description language-id="en_US">Displays a dropdown navigation menu with root menu items shown as buttons.</Description><Description language-id="zh_CN">\u663e\u793a\u4e0b\u62c9\u5f0f\u5bfc\u822a\u83dc\u5355\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u6839\u83dc\u5355\u9879\u663e\u793a\u4e3a\u6309\u94ae\u3002</Description><Description language-id="es_ES">Muestra un men\u00fa de navegaci\u00f3n desplegable con elementos de men\u00fa ra\u00edz que se muestran como botones.</Description><Description language-id="nl_NL">Geeft een rolmenu voor navigatie weer met rootmenu-items in de vorm van knoppen.</Description></root>','display',NULL,'ftl','<#includ